replies.body:
I feel like these changes would ultimently bring too much power to champs that just power farm {{champion:120}} {{champion:102}} . while i do like the idea of less opressive champs in the jungle, im not sure if this is the way to go about it.

On another point Scuttle crab is the worst change ive ever seen, i feel like its super biased to champs with cc to knock the armour off, and enough damage to kill it quick after.

Finally, with all the rune changes, I feel like they should fix that system first before messing with the jg. Think about preadator clear. Its insane on anyone who can run it {{champion:72}} , and encurages other oppressive jgs to counter it {{champion:64}} {{champion:35}}
